    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "For others experiencing this error, make sure your RPC ports are not open to the public.\r\n\r\nIf they are open to the public, you may find your RPC port getting spammed by attackers hoping to withdraw your funds. This spamming can cause you to lose your connection, resulting in the \"socket hang up\" error.",
